				<span class="body"><a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/israel-mossad-north-orea/" rel="category tag">Israel Mossad North orea</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/middle-east/" rel="category tag">Middle East</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/north-korea/" rel="category tag">North Korea</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/north-korea-arms-trafficking/" rel="category tag">North Korea arms trafficking</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/north-korea-spy/" rel="category tag">North Korea Spy</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/tag/north-korea-syria/" rel="category tag">North Korea Syria</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/north-korea-syria-israel/" rel="category tag">North Korea Syria Israel</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/north-korean-covert-operations/" rel="category tag">North Korean covert operations</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/north-korean-missiles/" rel="category tag">North Korean Missiles</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/north-korean-nuclear-program/" rel="category tag">North Korean Nuclear Program</a>, <a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/category/syria-mossad-north-korea-assassinations/" rel="category tag">Syria Mossad North Korea assassinations</a></span>
