<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_833" style="width: 500px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-833" data-attachment-id="833" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/26/frequent-flyers-guide-to-north-korean-air-a-review-of-worlds-only-one-star-airline/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg" data-orig-size="650,461" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="A Vomit Bag from North Korea" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg?w=490" class="size-full wp-image-833" alt="For your refuses vomit bag" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg?w=490&#038;h=347" width="490" height="347" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg?w=490&amp;h=347 490w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg?w=150&amp;h=106 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg?w=300&amp;h=213 300w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/a-vomit-bag-from-north-korea.jpg 650w" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-833" class="wp-caption-text">For your refuses vomit bag</p></div>
<p>The website airlinemeals.com, a service devoted to rating in flight food quality on every commercial air carrier on earth, devotes a whole section to passenger reviews of Air Koryo’s cuisine.</p>
<p>Route:         Beijing to Pyongyang, 2005-08-12</p>
<p>Flight duration:    1h 30m</p>
<p>Flight class:          economy</p>
<p>Ticket price:         n/a</p>
<p>Aircraft:      IL</p>
<p>Meal:          lunch &#8211; See the pic. No products are of any known brand or known style: it&#8217;s all &#8216;North Korean&#8217; in style.</p>
<p>Drink:         Water approved by the Great Leader</p>
<p>Comments:           Large portions. The sausages did have hard parts in it (bone?).</p>
<p>Rating (1-10):       5 stars</p>
<p><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="829" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/01/26/frequent-flyers-guide-to-north-korean-air-a-review-of-worlds-only-one-star-airline/koryo5meal/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg" data-orig-size="400,300" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="koryo5meal" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg?w=400" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-829" alt="koryo5meal" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg 400w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg?w=150 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/koryo5meal.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px"   /></a></p>
<p>In another review the meals slightly improved it seems.</p>
